{
  "id": "news-clipping",
  "name": "报纸剪报",
  "category": "news",
  "description": "一张从报纸上剪下来的新闻剪报，带有手写批注和咖啡渍",
  "trigger": {
    "type": "random",
    "probability": 0.02,
    "conditions": [
      {
        "type": "setting",
        "operator": "contains",
        "value": "悬疑|调查|侦探|新闻|媒体",
        "description": "悬疑或调查场景可能触发"
      },
      {
        "type": "story",
        "operator": "contains",
        "value": "报纸|新闻|报道|消息",
        "description": "剧情涉及新闻时可能触发"
      }
    ]
  },
  "variables": {
    "newsName": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "报纸名称"
    },
    "date": {
      "type": "date",
      "format": "YYYY年MM月DD日",
      "description": "新闻日期"
    },
    "title": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "新闻标题"
    },
    "content": {
      "type": "text",
      "maxLength": 400,
      "description": "新闻内容"
    },
    "section": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "版面/栏目"
    },
    "pageNumber": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "页码"
    },
    "note": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "手写批注内容"
    }
  },
  "promptTemplate": "请生成一份报纸剪报的内容。\n\n背景信息：\n- 场景：{{scene}}\n- 相关事件：{{event}}\n- 时间背景：{{timeContext}}\n\n要求：\n1. 新闻标题要吸引眼球\n2. 内容要符合故事背景设定\n3. 可以是重要新闻或有趣的小报道\n4. 手写批注要体现剪报保存者的关注点\n5. 字数控制在200-300字之间\n\n请直接输出剪报内容，不要有其他说明。",
  "style": {
    "theme": "investigative",
    "colors": ["#f5f5f0", "#1a1a1a", "#e74c3c"],
    "mood": "悬疑调查"
  },
  "rarity": "uncommon",
  "collectible": true
}